    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mind Vessel is a creature collection tactical autobattler about regrets and hope</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the void and fight the traumas of your spirits to find a way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392970/extras/5f947743abb3eb6b248508129daafef4.poster.avif?t=1771875975\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392970/extras/5f947743abb3eb6b248508129daafef4.webm?t=1771875975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392970/extras/5f947743abb3eb6b248508129daafef4.mp4?t=1771875975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Graft the body parts of your enemies on your spirits to gain various abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sacrifice spirits to graft their body parts to others and mix their abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392970/extras/fae9f0d8b11768adf173ba6c5e3804ae.poster.avif?t=1771875975\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392970/extras/fae9f0d8b11768adf173ba6c5e3804ae.webm?t=1771875975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392970/extras/fae9f0d8b11768adf173ba6c5e3804ae.mp4?t=1771875975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Push your score</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create powerful chain reactions to multiply your score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392970/extras/5616708c4fed2b13924261032220ee33.poster.avif?t=1771875975\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392970/extras/5616708c4fed2b13924261032220ee33.webm?t=1771875975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392970/extras/5616708c4fed2b13924261032220ee33.mp4?t=1771875975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Discover more about your spirits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your spirit's traumas and learn more about their story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392970/extras/3ab1bb082c3cf082f231755bacfc6b75.poster.avif?t=1771875975\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392970/extras/3ab1bb082c3cf082f231755bacfc6b75.webm?t=1771875975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392970/extras/3ab1bb082c3cf082f231755bacfc6b75.mp4?t=1771875975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A roguelite gameplay with metaprogression, seeded runs and 10 difficulty levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel 1 bit art style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 playable vessels with each their own unique playstyle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 spirits with their own backstory and specific abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ different mind stones with unique effects to build your strategy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Always push your best score higher with the endless mode</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
